'''Kylie Harris''' is an Australian actress and amateur model.

She has appeared in '''Jackson's Wharf''', '''Shortland Street''' and '''Skyrunners'''.

She appeared in [[Game of Thrones]] as [[Genna]], a prostitute in [[Petyr Baelish]]'s brothel in [[King's Landing]].
